cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation and language modeling. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses word embeddings and a log-bilinear softmax-based model. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves natural language processing and probabilistic modeling. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with improving the accuracy of machine translation systems. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it uses statistical machine translation systems which are often used in image captioning and other computer vision tasks.
